long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
udata 是由阿里巴巴数据技术及产品部提供的一款数据可视化插件，仅可在阿里巴巴内网使用。

udata致力于降低数据的访问门槛，提升数据的易用性。

如果您在内网环境下，访问页面符合阿里巴巴埋点规范且在域名白名单中，点击udata图标，即可启动udata。udata会在页面上显示埋点坑位的数据信息。

有任何问题或建议，请联系 行权，联系方式见内网，谢谢。

udata is a data visualization plugin provided by Alibaba's Data Technology and Product Department. It can only be used on the Alibaba intranet.

udata is committed to reducing the access threshold of data and improving the ease of use of the data.

If you are in an intranet environment, the page you visit conforms to Alibaba ’s buried site specifications and is in the domain name whitelist. Click the udata icon to start udata. udata will display the data information of the buried point on the page.

If you have any questions or suggestions, please contact 行权(247247), contact information is on the intranet, thank you.
